      "sourceStatus": "REDACTION_MARKER_CHECK",
      "sourceText": "You will recall that Mr. [REDACTED] advised the Bureau of a letter which Walter Winchell had received from an individual in Los Angeles indicating that he had seen a flying saucer leave the ground within his view and which letter he theorized that this might have been a landing from another planet.",
