      "lineNumber": 15,
      "sourceStatus": "REDACTION_MARKER_CHECK",
      "sourceText": "The Los Angeles Office has now advised that the [REDACTED] have no knowledge of any [REDACTED] and that other investigation to locate [REDACTED] was unproductive. It would appear, therefore, that this may have been a prank.",
